text: SC Makhachkala () is a Russian football team from Makhachkala. It was founded in 2019 by three people (including coach Gadzhi Gadzhiyev) and licensed for third-tier Russian Professional Football League for the 2019–20 season. ==Current squad== As of 17 October 2020, according to the PFL website. ==References== Category:Association football clubs established in 2019 Category:Football clubs in Russia Category:Sport in Makhachkala Category:2019 establishments in Russia
